thread.title: ‘Vijender will undoubtedly win pro debut bout’, says Raj Sangwan
thread.title_full: ‘Vijender will undoubtedly win pro debut bout’, says Raj Sangwan

author: NewsWire
title: ‘Vijender will undoubtedly win pro debut bout’, says Raj Sangwan
text:
0 0 0 0 0 
New Delhi, Oct.10 (ANI): Former professional boxer Raj Kumar Sangwan has expressed confidence over Vijender Singh performing well in his first professional bout at the Manchester Arena today. 
The two-time gold medalist further said that Vijender has all the required skills and experience needed to claim victory over Sonny Whiting. 
Arjuna Awardee Sanghwan also revealed that everyone is fond of professional boxing, as it involves a lot of drama, and added that fans like to see blood during the fight. 
Vijender, who has been training hard under Lee Beard over the last one month, will play his four-round debut fight against Whiting on Saturday. (ANI) 
By Vivek Prabhakar Singh
